                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2385" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0505</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8016 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百步亭集团：共创价值如何修炼社区综合服务商?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Baibuting Group: How to cultivate itself to be an alternative integrated service provider through co</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">柳娟，田志龙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百步亭集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">25 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社区综合服务商；共创价值；战略性企业社会责任；百步亭集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">integrated service provider; value co-creation; SCSR; Baibuting Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着房地产业“白银时代”到来，转型升级成为必然趋势，而社区综合服务商是其中主流选择。不少专注传统建筑业的房地产企业根据自身规模纷纷提出转型方案并做出尝试。但是如何实现从建造商到服务商的华丽变身将是该行业面临的一个长期挑战。本案例全面梳理了百步亭集团20年以“问题为导向”深耕细作一个全国闻名的大型社区的进程和脉络，介绍了集团以共创价值的方式在社区构建全方位的管理服务体系过程中遇到的复杂问题和挑战，并对百步亭集团在解决这些挑战中不断构建或嵌入社区管理和服务平台，通过融合政府、社会和市场三方力量的方式，从建设、管理、服务全产业链上构建价值闭环体系的过程进行了清晰的描述。对该案例进行探讨和分析，可以充分地将共创价值过程理论和战略性企业社会责任理论与百步亭集团构建社区综合服务商的过程实践相融合，有利于促进学员对所涉及理论的把握，并将其灵活的运用于案例分析中，也对其他房地产企业转型和可持续发展具有一定的借鉴和参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the real estate industry drops into silver age, transformation and upgrading seems to be the inevitable trend for most real estate companies. And to be integrated service provider in community is preferred choice for most firms who had been focused on construction business. How to upgrade successful has been a concern and challenge for a upgrading firm in a long term. This case has described the process of how Baibuting group make great efforts to raise a large community with problem-orientation logic. Then the problems and challenges met by the group has been articulated and the key cooperative initiatives and process that has been used in building an overall service system with the force of government and society also have been described clearly in this case. When the teacher and student discuss and analyze the case, the value co-creation theory and strategic corporate social responsibility framework should be combined with the cultivating practice to be integrated service provider for Baibuting Group. It will be helpful for the discussant to grasp the theories involved in the case and put these theories used in the analysis of the case. At the same time, it also will be benefit to students use these theories and practice methods in the upgrading of other real estate firms.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《商业伦理与社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业与社会之间的关系、共创价值、战略性企业社会责任、利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
